| **Operation**               | **What the Operation Does**                         | **Data Structure Used** | **Why This DS Is Suitable**                                                    | **How User Interacts**                                                    |
| --------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Push Item** (Sarim)       | Naya item stack ke top par add hota hai.            | Stack                   | LIFO structure fast insertion aur undo-type features ke liye perfect hota hai. | User “Add Item” button press karta hai → item top me add ho jata hai.     |
| **Pop Item** (Sarim)        | Stack se last added item remove hota hai.           | Stack                   | Stack last element ko instantly remove karne ki ability deta hai.              | User “Remove Last” press karta hai → top item remove ho jata hai.         |
